## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-124">使用完畢後，您都要呼叫 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> 以關閉 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> 執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-124">You should always close a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> instance by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> when finished working with it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-125">這樣可能會更快地釋放系統資源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-125">This allows system resources to potentially be freed sooner.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-126">如果已呼叫 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message.CreateBufferedCopy%2A> 以建立訊息的訊息緩衝區，並且使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.CreateMessage%2A> 檢查訊息，當您嘗試使用這個方法關閉緩衝區時，就會發生 <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-126">If you have called <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message.CreateBufferedCopy%2A> to create a message buffer of a message, and inspected the message using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.CreateMessage%2A>, you will get a <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> when you attempt to close the buffer using this method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-127">為了避免這個問題發生，您要先從緩衝區重新建立訊息，然後再關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-127">To avoid this problem, you need to recreate the message from the buffer before closing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-128">如需先前案例的示範以及解決這個問題的方法，請參閱＜範例＞一節中的程式碼範例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-128">See the code sample in the Example section for a demonstration of the previous scenario and a way to resolve this problem.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c63f-129">下列範例示範如何正確關閉訊息緩衝區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c63f-129">The following example demonstrates how to properly close a message buffer.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void AfterReceiveReply(ref Message reply, object correlationState)  
{  
    // Create the buffer  
    MessageBuffer buffer = reply.CreateBufferedCopy(13000);  
    // Inspect the response (for example, extract the body contents)  
    Message thisReply = buffer.CreateMessage();  
    XmlDictionaryReader reader = thisReply.GetReaderAtBodyContents();  
    StringBuilder info = new StringBuilder();  
    XmlWriter writer = XmlWriter.Create(info);  
    writer.WriteNode(reader, true);  
    writer.Close();  
    // Resolution:  Re-create the message from the buffer before  
    // closing.  
    reply = buffer.CreateMessage();  
    // You can close the buffer after the message has been recreated.  
    buffer.Close();  
```  
  
